		<description>
                Chandrayaan-2 Dual Frequency SAR operates in StripMap mode with a nominal swath of 10 Km.
                Data is acquired in various modes i.e. Circular/Dual/Quad(Full Polarimetric).
                The antenna beam-limited footprint varies from about 22.5 Km to 34 Km for L-band and from 11.2 Km to 16.8 Km for S-band, over the range coverage region from 16 Km to 70 Km off-nadir.
